OL,3,CGovernment 'failed' to act on patient
OL,4,Csafety recommendation
OL,6,FThe government has failed to implement
OL,7,Fa number of recommendations over major
OL,8,Fpatient safety issues, according to an
OL,9,Findependent panel.
OL,11,FThe report, commissioned by the Health
OL,12,Fand Social Committee in the wake of
OL,13,Fthe case, voiced concerns about
OL,14,F"delays to take real action".
OL,16,FAs part of its investigation, the
OL,17,Fpanel selected recommendations from
OL,18,Findependent public inquiries and
OL,19,Freviews that have been accepted by
OL,20,Fgovernment since 2010.
