OL,6,FThe recommendations on maternity care
OL,7,Fand leadership came from the 2013
OL,8,Freport that followed a public inquiry
OL,9,Finto patient deaths at the Mid
OL,10,FStaffordshire NHS Foundation Trust, as
OL,11,Fwell as the 2015 report from the
OL,12,FMorecambe Bay Investigation, which
OL,13,Fhighlighted serious failings at the
OL,14,FUniversity Hospitals of Morecambe Bay
OL,15,FNHS Foundation Trust leading to the
OL,16,Fdeaths of mothers and babies.
OL,18,FThe panel gave the government a rating
OL,19,Fof "requires improvement" across the
OL,20,Fpolicy areas. One of the
OL,21,Frecommendations was rated good.
