OL,6,FThe report said that "despite good
OL,7,Fperformance in some areas" the rating
OL,8,F"partly reflects the length of time it
OL,9,Fhas taken for the government to make
OL,10,Fprogress on fully implementing four of
OL,11,Fthe recommendations which were
OL,12,Faccepted nine years ago, or longer".
OL,14,F"Progress is imminent in several
OL,15,Fareas, which is reassuring, but we
OL,16,Fremain concerned about the time it has
OL,17,Ftaken for real action to be taken," it
OL,18,Fadded.
