OL,6,FThe panel did recognise the impact the
OL,7,FCovid-19 pandemic may have had on
OL,8,Fimplementing recommendations.
OL,10,FProfessor Dame Jane Dacre, chair of
OL,11,Fthe expert panel, said: "Nine or more
OL,12,Fyears have passed since these
OL,13,Frecommendations were accepted by the
OL,14,Fgovernment of the day.
OL,16,F"We are concerned about delays to take
OL,17,Freal action to implement them and rate
OL,18,Foverall progress by the government on
OL,19,Fthis serious matter as requiring
OL,20,Fimprovement."
