OL,6,FThe report added the aim of using
OL,7,F"evidence-based scrutiny" is to "feed
OL,8,Fback to those making promises so that
OL,9,Fthey can assess whether their
OL,10,Fcommitments ` or in this case, the
OL,11,Fimplementation of recommendations the
OL,12,Fgovernment has accepted ` are on track
OL,13,Fto be met".
OL,15,FSteve Brine, chairman of the Health
OL,16,Fand Social Committee, welcomed the
OL,17,Freport, which he said was
OL,18,F"commissioned in the wake of the deep
OL,19,Fconcern around the Letby case which
OL,20,Fgave rise to calls for another
OL,21,Fstatutory inquiry".
