OL,6,FMr Brine added: "The Health and Social
OL,7,FCare Committee has now launched its
OL,8,Finquiry into leadership, performance
OL,9,Fand patient safety in the NHS. The
OL,10,Fwork of the panel will provide
OL,11,Fvaluable insights and an important
OL,12,Ffoundation in support of our
OL,13,Fforthcoming public evidence sessions."
OL,15,FPublication of the panel's findings
OL,16,Fcomes after NHS Whistleblowers, a
OL,17,Fgroup representing hundreds of current
OL,18,Fand former doctors, midwives and
OL,19,Fnurses, asked to contribute to the
OL,20,FLucy Letby inquiry.
