OL,6,F"We recently announced the first phase
OL,7,Fof Martha's Rule which will give
OL,8,Fpatients or family members in 100 NHS
OL,9,Fsites the right to a rapid review of
OL,10,Ftheir care if they are concerned their
OL,11,Fcondition is worsening," they said.
OL,13,F"We have also established an
OL,14,Findependent body to investigate and
OL,15,Flearn from serious patient safety
OL,16,Fincidents, and we have made progress
OL,17,Fin improving maternity services,
OL,18,Freducing the stillbirth and neonatal
OL,19,Fdeath rate by 23% and 30% respectively
OL,20,Fsince 2010."
